<TEXT>
<P>
JOHANNESBURG, April 10 (Xinhua) -- The recent discovery of a
huge natural gas field off South Africa's west coast will prompt
the country to build its first gas-fired power station in Cape
Town within the next five years, said Western Cape Province
Premier Gerald Morkel on Monday.
</P>
