Works and Highways, is the first phase of NRIMP, a nine-year
sustained program of assistance by the World Bank.
</P>
<P>
The NRIMP aims to support the government's reform program in
the road sector, which seeks to address management and financing
issues of national roads.
</P>
<P>
The loan has a maturity of 20 years. 
