<HEADLINE> One-China Principle, Prerequisite of Improved Cross-Straits Relations: Magazine (3) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The magazine relates that ever since semi-official channels of
communication were formed, all dialogue and negotiations between
the two sides have been based on the one-China principle.
</P>
<P>
