was quoted Saturday by the press as saying that the total
investment includes the production of the Focus model, the
manufacture of new pieces in the Pacheco plant, a new painting
plant, the redesigning of the Ford Escort, a new motor or the
Ranger pickup truck, and other disbursements in security and
environment. (Ford-Argentina) 
