<HEADLINE> Chelsea Beats Newcastle in FA Cup Semi-final </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, April 9 (Xinhua) -- Two goals by Gustavo Poyet earned
Chelsea a place in the FA Cup final alongside Aston Villa after a
scintillating semi against Newcastle United at Wembley on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
