</P>
<P>
Instead, "there is a problem and there is a crisis" in the peace
march, Moussa said while briefing reporters on the Mubarak-Barak
talks, which the minister said dwelt on the situation on the
Syrian, Palestinian and Lebanese tracks. (Egypt-Israel-Mideast
